# Custom Rules

## Browser Verification Policy
- DO NOT perform browser verification or testing (using browser subagent, opening urls in browser, etc.) under any circumstances.
- This is to avoid slowing down operations and wasting tokens.

## LFmall NEW Exhibition Template Rules (Reference: C:\event_guide)
- Refer to `C:\event_guide` (specifically `rules.md` and `design.md`) for specifications regarding the LFmall [기획전 NEW템플릿] system.
- When rendering mockups/previews:
  - Adhere to the Cohere premium design tokens (`var(--near-black)`, `var(--canvas-white)`, `var(--coral)`, `var(--soft-stone)`).
  - PC/Mobile preview headers must be consistently labeled as `"PC 미리보기"` and `"Mobile 미리보기"`.
  - Maintain viewport isolation and layout responsiveness without using hardcoded maximum widths that break container limits.
  - Apply standard LFmall Typography (`font-family: "Malgun Gothic", "Apple SD Gothic Neo", sans-serif;`, letter-spacing, line-height) and Siganture Colors (black `#000000`, gray `#111111`, coral `#e25822`).
  - Keep UTF-8 with BOM (EF BB BF) encoding for files to avoid character corruption.
